<P>TO THE HONOURABLE AND RIGHT REVEREND JOHN EGERTON, LORD BISHOP OF DURHAM, THE FOLLOWING Hi&s;tory of the County Palatine of Durham, (THE MITRE OF WHICH HIS LORDSHIP WEARS WITH A GRACE AND DIGNITY BECOMING SO DISTINGUISHED A SEE), IS MOST HUMBLY INSCRIBED AND DEDICATED, AS A MARK OF GRATITUDE, AND OF REVERENCE FOR HIS CHARACTER, BY The AUTHOR.</P>
