<P>Burgen&s;es Dunelmi reddunt compotum de c <HI>s.</HI> de placitis Eu&s;tacii filii Johannis. In the&s;auro xl <HI>s.</HI> Et in perdonis per breve regis ei&s;dem burgen&s;ibus, xl <HI>s. pro cumbu&s;tione domuum &s;uarum.</HI> Et quieti &s;unt.</P>
