<P>Memd. that ye xxvijth day of Juyne the ixth yere of the con&s;ecrac'on of the reverend fadre in God Tho. bu&s;hop of Dure&s;me, I John Bukke vewer to my &s;aid lord of Durham, &amp;c.</P>
