<P>Item, the makyng of a greate cheyne that Mr Page my lordis &s;arvaunt ware at my lordis commandement when my lorde went to Callice &amp; my lorde of Duri&s;&s;yne <HI>(Durham)</HI> with odar, wheche cheyne wayid <HI>cc</HI> <ABBR>l.</ABBR> of myne oune golde wheche gold I re&s;ceavyd agen re&s;te to me for the makyng <HI>xl</HI> <ABBR>s.</ABBR></P>
